title: Fred Falke - Remixes Compilation
description:
Hello, I saw that there wasn't a Remix Compilation in the whole internet of this glorious man. So I decided to recollect all of his remixes and share with the comunity.



Most of the tracks are beetween 192-320kbps. I tried to get every single track in the best quality.



Screenshot of the tracks: http://img.imgur.com/UNRG9Mx.jpg



And if you love some song, support the artist and buy it on iTunes/BeatPort,etc...

Hope you enjoy it!
